 <group name="hipay">
  <string name="module_description"><![CDATA[This is the Hipay Wallet Payment solution; Be sure to register at Hipay to get a live and a sandbox account.<p>Don't forget that you need cURL and SimpleXML installed on your server.</p><p><a href="https://www.hipaywallet.com" target="_blank">You need an Hipay Account?</a></p><p>Please ensure to set a string at "Code to encrypt Callback" with more than 5 digits.</p><p>You need to have cURL and SimpleXML enabled at your server.</p>]]></string>
